{"tid":712350,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［唔使等iOS 12］Google量度程式Measure更新至2.0 支援ARCore裝置 即大部分Android旗艦","createTime":"2018-06-22T04:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T04:03:36.000Z","uid":1714,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3dc5f2f5952d30757835100967730e17fd74505e","tid":712350,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-yHmGVDbqU-M/WyxaqOuXhOI/AAAAAAABlDE/DK5WcjH8B_oyJ1gzTNQc8MlL_r5EJ-6xwCLcBGAs/s1600/measurebygoogle.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-yHmGVDbqU-M%2FWyxaqOuXhOI%2FAAAAAAABlDE%2FDK5WcjH8B_oyJ1gzTNQc8MlL_r5EJ-6xwCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Fmeasurebygoogle.png&h=2f38941b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">iOS 12入面有一個新程式叫Measure，佢係用AR技術，用戶可以用電話對住實物，好輕易咁量度到一件物件嘅尺寸，而且非常準確。雖然普通用戶唔會好常用，但到要用嘅時候就會覺得好實用。有唔少Android用戶都對呢個app有興趣，但遺憾冇Android廠商有推出呢個功能。雖然Google Play Store上面有好多類似嘅程式，但質素有參差，唔及Apple出嗰個咁好。 <br />\n<br />\nGoogle都唔執輸，今日將旗下都係叫Measure嘅量度程式更新到版本2.0，支援所有支援ARCore嘅Android裝置，即大部分旗艦Android手機，用戶可以用個程式，準確咁量度實物嘅尺寸，唔需要再羨慕iOS用戶，更何況iOS 12正式版約九月尾先會發佈， 可以話Android嘅用戶今次捷足先登。 </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">iFan又少個機會打J</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6101f4476f2bf8edbff4689e61262c2a198304","tid":712350,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:42:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thealpha.app/2018/06/measurebygoogle.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thealpha.app%2F2018%2F06%2Fmeasurebygoogle.html%3Fm%3D1&d=%2BRw2xM0Hd4f155oiEcL3Q26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=9747464d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thealpha.app/2018/06/measurebygoogle.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"2f3f42d5659765f27ca5520e06343b172169c1ad","tid":712350,"uid":1886,"like":9,"disli